<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Tu Merienda — Meriendas frescas, felices y sin complicaciones</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Baloo+2:wght@500;700;800&family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Caveat:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --cream:#7FEFD1;
    --sky:#FFDD57;
    --sky-deep:#FFC300;
    --navy:#262B7A;
    --navy-ink:#1B1F4B;
    --teal:#2FB6C4;
    --magenta:#EC1E8C;
    --marigold:#F5A623;
    --tomato:#E63946;
    --line:#20244f;
    --card:#FFFFFF;
    --shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--navy-ink);
    --shadow-sm: 4px 4px 0 var(--navy-ink);
    --radius: 28px;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    font-family:'Nunito', sans-serif;
    color:var(--navy-ink);
    background:var(--sky);
    overflow-x:hidden;
    line-height:1.5;
  }
  h1,h2,h3, .display{
    font-family:'Baloo 2', sans-serif;
    line-height:1.1;
  }
  .hand{ font-family:'Caveat', cursive; }
  img{max-width:100%; display:block;}
  a{color:inherit;}
  .wrap{ max-width:1180px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 28px; }
  section{ position:relative; }

  /* ---------- Nav ---------- */
  header{
    position:sticky; top:0; z-index:50;
    background:rgba(255,251,241,0.88);
    backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
    border-bottom:3px solid var(--line);
  }
  nav.wrap{
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    padding:12px 28px;
  }
  .brand{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; font-family:'Baloo 2'; font-weight:800; font-size:1.35rem; color:var(--navy);}
  .brand img{ height:44px; width:auto; }
  nav ul{ list-style:none; display:flex; gap:28px; }
  nav ul a{ text-decoration:none; font-weight:700; font-size:.98rem; color:var(--navy-ink); position:relative; padding:6px 2px;}
  nav ul a:after{ content:""; position:absolute; left:0; right:0; bottom:-2px; height:3px; background:var(--marigold); transform:scaleX(0); transform-origin:left; transition:transform .25s ease;}
  nav ul a:hover:after{ transform:scaleX(1); }
  .nav-cta{
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
    background:var(--magenta); color:#fff; font-family:'Baloo 2'; font-weight:700;
    padding:10px 20px; border-radius:999px; border:3px solid var(--line);
    box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); text-decoration:none; font-size:.95rem;
    transition:transform .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover{ transform:translate(-2px,-2px); box-shadow:6px 6px 0 var(--navy-ink); }
  .nav-toggle{ display:none; }

  /* ---------- Buttons ---------- */
  .btn{
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; justify-content:center;
    font-family:'Baloo 2'; font-weight:700; font-size:1.02rem;
    padding:14px 30px; border-radius:999px; border:3px solid var(--line);
    text-decoration:none; cursor:pointer; box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    transition:transform .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease;
  }
  .btn:hover{ transform:translate(-3px,-3px); box-shadow:9px 9px 0 var(--navy-ink); }
  .btn:active{ transform:translate(0,0); box-shadow:2px 2px 0 var(--navy-ink); }
  .btn-primary{ background:var(--marigold); color:var(--navy-ink); }
  .btn-secondary{ background:#fff; color:var(--navy-ink); }
  .btn-teal{ background:var(--teal); color:#fff; }

  /* ---------- Hero ---------- */
  .hero{
    padding:70px 0 40px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 12%, #fff6d8 0%, transparent 42%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--sky) 0%, var(--sky-deep) 100%);
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .hero .wrap{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr; gap:40px; align-items:center; }
  .eyebrow{
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
    background:#fff; border:3px solid var(--line); border-radius:999px;
    padding:6px 16px; font-weight:800; font-size:.82rem; letter-spacing:.03em;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:18px;
  }
  .eyebrow .dot{ width:9px; height:9px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--tomato); }
  .hero h1{
    font-size:clamp(2.3rem, 4.4vw, 3.6rem); color:var(--navy); font-weight:800;
    margin-bottom:18px;
  }
  .hero h1 span{ color:var(--magenta); }
  .hero p.lead{ font-size:1.18rem; max-width:46ch; margin-bottom:30px; color:#333a63; }
  .hero-actions{ display:flex; gap:16px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:26px; }
  .trust-row{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; font-weight:700; font-size:.92rem; color:var(--navy);}
  .trust-row .avatars{ display:flex; }
  .trust-row .avatars span{
    width:34px; height:34px; border-radius:50%; border:3px solid var(--sky);
    margin-left:-10px; display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-size:1rem; background:var(--marigold);
  }
  .trust-row .avatars span:first-child{ margin-left:0; background:var(--teal); }
  .trust-row .avatars span:nth-child(2){ background:var(--magenta); }

  .hero-art{ position:relative; display:flex; justify-content:center; align-items:center; }
  .hero-art .logo-badge{
    position:relative; z-index:3; width:min(340px, 82%);
    filter:drop-shadow(8px 10px 0 rgba(27,31,75,0.18));
    animation: float 5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .hero-art .cloud{ position:absolute; opacity:.9; }
  .hero-art .sun{ position:absolute; top:-6%; right:2%; width:90px; opacity:.85; animation: spin 26s linear infinite; }
  @keyframes float{ 0%,100%{ transform:translateY(0);} 50%{ transform:translateY(-14px);} }
  @keyframes spin{ from{ transform:rotate(0);} to{ transform:rotate(360deg);} }

  .wave{
    display:block; width:100%; height:auto; margin-top:-2px;
  }

  /* ---------- Section headers ---------- */
  .section-head{ text-align:center; max-width:640px; margin:0 auto 46px; }
  .section-head .eyebrow{ margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; }
  .section-head h2{ font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.5rem); color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:14px; }
  .section-head p{ color:#3d436e; font-size:1.05rem; }

  /* ---------- Cómo funciona ---------- */
  .como{ background:var(--cream); padding:90px 0; border-top:3px solid var(--line); border-bottom:3px solid var(--line);}
  .steps{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:28px; counter-reset:step; }
  .step{
    background:var(--card); border:3px solid var(--line); border-radius:var(--radius);
    padding:30px 26px; box-shadow:var(--shadow); position:relative;
  }
  .step .num{
    font-family:'Baloo 2'; font-weight:800; font-size:1rem; color:#fff;
    background:var(--teal); width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:50%;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; border:3px solid var(--line);
    margin-bottom:16px;
  }
  .step:nth-child(2) .num{ background:var(--magenta); }
  .step:nth-child(3) .num{ background:var(--marigold); }
  .step h3{ font-size:1.25rem; color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:8px; }
  .step p{ color:#454b74; font-size:.98rem; }

  /* ---------- Snack Attack ---------- */
  .snack{
    background:#F5A623;
    background:linear-gradient(180deg,#FFD873 0%, #F5A623 100%);
    color:var(--navy-ink); padding:100px 0 90px; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  }
  .snack:before, .snack:after{
    content:""; position:absolute; left:0; right:0; height:26px;
    background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, #1B1F4B 25%, transparent 25%), linear-gradient(-45deg, #1B1F4B 25%, transparent 25%);
    background-size:26px 26px; opacity:.08;
  }
  .snack:before{ top:0; } .snack:after{ bottom:0; }
  .snack-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:.9fr 1.1fr; gap:56px; align-items:center; }
  .snack-badge-wrap{ display:flex; justify-content:center; }
  .snack-badge{
    width:min(360px,88%); border-radius:50%; border:6px solid #fff;
    box-shadow:0 0 0 6px var(--navy-ink), var(--shadow);
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .snack .eyebrow{ background:var(--navy-ink); border-color:var(--navy-ink); color:#FFE29B; }
  .snack .eyebrow .dot{ background:var(--magenta); }
  .snack h2{ font-family:'Baloo 2'; font-size:clamp(1.9rem,3.4vw,2.7rem); margin-bottom:16px; }
  .snack h2 span{ color:var(--magenta); }
  .snack p.lead{ font-size:1.08rem; color:#3d436e; max-width:52ch; margin-bottom:26px;}
  .chip-row{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:12px; margin-bottom:30px; }
  .chip{
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; background:rgba(27,31,75,.08);
    border:2px solid var(--navy-ink); border-radius:999px; padding:9px 16px;
    font-weight:700; font-size:.9rem; color:var(--navy-ink);
  }

  /* ---------- Menú semanal (captura de la app) ---------- */
  .lonchera-section{ padding:100px 0; background:var(--sky); }
  .menu-shot-wrap{ display:flex; justify-content:center; }
  .phone-frame{
    max-width:360px; width:100%; border:5px solid var(--line); border-radius:38px;
    overflow:hidden; box-shadow:var(--shadow); background:#fff;
  }
  .menu-shot{ display:block; width:100%; }
  .note-love{ font-family:'Caveat'; font-size:1.3rem; color:var(--tomato); margin-top:-6px;}

  /* ---------- Planes ---------- */
  .planes{ padding:100px 0; background:var(--cream); border-top:3px solid var(--line); border-bottom:3px solid var(--line);}
  .plans-showcase{
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:40px; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:center;
    max-width:980px; margin:0 auto;
  }
  .plans-mascot{ position:relative; flex:0 0 auto; }
  .plans-mascot-img{
    width:150px; height:150px; border-radius:50%; object-fit:cover;
    border:5px solid #fff; box-shadow:0 0 0 5px var(--line), var(--shadow);
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .mascot-bubble{
    position:absolute; top:-14px; right:-58px; background:#fff; border:3px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:999px; padding:8px 16px; font-family:'Baloo 2'; font-weight:700; font-size:.85rem;
    box-shadow:3px 3px 0 var(--navy-ink); white-space:nowrap;
  }
  .mascot-bubble:before{
    content:""; position:absolute; left:-10px; bottom:10px; width:0; height:0;
    border-top:8px solid transparent; border-bottom:8px solid transparent; border-right:10px solid var(--line);
  }
  .plan-pills{ list-style:none; display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:14px; max-width:560px; }
  .plan-pill{
    font-family:'Baloo 2'; font-weight:700; font-size:1rem; color:var(--navy-ink);
    background:#fff; border:3px solid var(--line); border-radius:999px; padding:12px 22px;
    box-shadow:3px 3px 0 var(--navy-ink);
  }
  .plan-pill:nth-child(1){ background:#E9F6F7; }
  .plan-pill:nth-child(2){ background:#FDEAF4; }
  .plan-pill:nth-child(3){ background:#FFF3DE; }
  .plan-pill:nth-child(4){ background:#FDE7E8; }
  .plan-pill:nth-child(5){ background:var(--navy); color:#fff; }

  /* ---------- Testimonios ---------- */
  .testi{ padding:90px 0; background:var(--sky); }
  .testi-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:24px; }
  .testi-card{
    background:#fff; border:3px solid var(--line); border-radius:22px; padding:26px;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  .testi-card p{ font-size:.98rem; color:#3d436e; margin-bottom:16px; }
  .testi-who{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; font-weight:800; font-family:'Baloo 2'; color:var(--navy); }
  .testi-who .av{ width:42px; height:42px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--teal); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#fff; font-size:1.2rem; border:2px solid var(--line);}

  /* ---------- CTA final ---------- */
  .cta-final{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--magenta), var(--tomato));
    color:#fff; padding:90px 0; text-align:center; border-top:3px solid var(--line);
  }
  .cta-final h2{ font-size:clamp(1.9rem,3.6vw,2.7rem); margin-bottom:16px; }
  .cta-final p{ max-width:50ch; margin:0 auto 30px; font-size:1.08rem; opacity:.95; }
  .cta-form{ display:flex; gap:10px; max-width:460px; margin:0 auto; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:center;}
  .cta-form input{
    flex:1; min-width:220px; padding:14px 18px; border-radius:999px; border:3px solid var(--line);
    font-family:'Nunito'; font-weight:700; font-size:1rem; outline:none;
  }
  .cta-note{ margin-top:16px; font-size:.85rem; opacity:.85; }
  .whatsapp-btn{ display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; }
  .form-msg{ margin-top:16px; font-weight:800; font-family:'Baloo 2'; display:none; }
  .form-msg.show{ display:block; }

  /* ---------- Footer ---------- */
  footer{ background:#DCEEFB; color:#2b3a55; padding:56px 0 26px; border-top:3px solid var(--line); }
  .foot-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr 1fr; gap:40px; margin-bottom:40px; }
  .foot-brand{ display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; font-family:'Baloo 2'; font-weight:800; font-size:1.25rem; color:var(--navy-ink); margin-bottom:14px;}
  .foot-brand img{ height:36px; }
  footer h4{ font-family:'Baloo 2'; color:var(--navy-ink); margin-bottom:14px; font-size:1rem;}
  footer ul{ list-style:none; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; font-size:.92rem;}
  footer ul a{ text-decoration:none; color:#2b3a55; }
  footer ul a:hover{ color:var(--tomato); }
  .foot-bottom{ border-top:1px solid rgba(27,31,75,.15); padding-top:22px; font-size:.82rem; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; color:#5c6a8a;}

  /* ---------- Reveal on scroll ---------- */
  .reveal{ opacity:0; transform:translateY(24px); transition:opacity .6s ease, transform .6s ease; }
  .reveal.in{ opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    *{ animation:none !important; transition:none !important; }
  }

  /* ---------- Responsive ---------- */
  @media (max-width: 960px){
    .hero .wrap{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .hero-art{ order:-1; }
    .steps{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .snack-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .snack-badge-wrap{ order:-1; }
    .plan-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .plan-card.featured{ transform:none; }
    .testi-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .foot-grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .lunchbox-body{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    nav ul{ display:none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <nav class="wrap">
    <div class="brand"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Tu Merienda"> Tu Merienda</div>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#como-funciona">Cómo funciona</a></li>
      <li><a href="#snack-attack">Snack Attack</a></li>
      <li><a href="#menu">Menú semanal</a></li>
      <li><a href="#planes">Planes</a></li>
    </ul>
    <a href="#registro" class="nav-cta">Quiero mi merienda</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span> App de meriendas por suscripción</div>
      <h1>Meriendas frescas y felices, <span>listas cada día</span></h1>
      <p class="lead">Elige un plan, personaliza los gustos de tu familia y recibe meriendas preparadas con ingredientes frescos, ricos y nutritivos. Sin planear, sin complicarte, todos los días.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#registro" class="btn btn-primary">Quiero mi merienda 🍓</a>
        <a href="#como-funciona" class="btn btn-secondary">Ver cómo funciona</a>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-row">
        <div class="avatars"><span>🧑</span><span>👩</span><span>🧒</span></div>
        Familias que ya no improvisan la merienda de sus hijos
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-art">
      <svg class="sun" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><circle cx="50" cy="50" r="24" fill="#F5A623" opacity="0.9"/><g stroke="#F5A623" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.9"><line x1="50" y1="2" x2="50" y2="16"/><line x1="50" y1="84" x2="50" y2="98"/><line x1="2" y1="50" x2="16" y2="50"/><line x1="84" y1="50" x2="98" y2="50"/><line x1="15" y1="15" x2="24" y2="24"/><line x1="76" y1="76" x2="85" y2="85"/><line x1="85" y1="15" x2="76" y2="24"/><line x1="24" y1="76" x2="15" y2="85"/></g></svg>
      <svg class="cloud" style="width:110px; top:6%; left:-6%;" viewBox="0 0 200 120"><path d="M40 90 Q10 90 10 65 Q10 42 34 42 Q38 18 66 18 Q92 18 98 42 Q124 42 124 66 Q124 90 96 90 Z" fill="#fff"/></svg>
      <svg class="cloud" style="width:90px; bottom:2%; right:-4%;" viewBox="0 0 200 120"><path d="M40 90 Q10 90 10 65 Q10 42 34 42 Q38 18 66 18 Q92 18 98 42 Q124 42 124 66 Q124 90 96 90 Z" fill="#fff"/></svg>
      <img class="logo-badge" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Logo Tu Merienda">
    </div>
  </div>
  <svg class="wave" viewBox="0 0 1440 90" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="M0,32 C240,80 480,0 720,24 C960,48 1200,88 1440,40 L1440,90 L0,90 Z" fill="#FFFBF1"/></svg>
</section>

<!-- COMO FUNCIONA -->
<section class="como" id="como-funciona">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span> Así de simple</div>
      <h2>Tres pasos y listo</h2>
      <p>Desde la app Tu Merienda armas la rutina de meriendas de tu familia en minutos.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="num">1</div>
        <h3>Elige tu plan</h3>
        <p>Escoge la frecuencia y cantidad de meriendas que necesita tu familia. Estamos siempre listos donde más nos necesites.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="num">2</div>
        <h3>Personaliza los gustos</h3>
        <p>Escoge qué meriendas quieres comer entre una salada, dulce, postre, fruta, jugo o refresco.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step reveal">
        <div class="num">3</div>
        <h3>Recíbela fresca</h3>
        <p>Tu merienda llega lista, cada día, preparada con ingredientes frescos y mucho cariño.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SNACK ATTACK -->
<section class="snack" id="snack-attack">
  <div class="wrap snack-grid">
    <div class="snack-badge-wrap reveal">
      <img class="snack-badge" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Snack Attack by Tu Merienda">
    </div>
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span> Primer lanzamiento</div>
      <h2>Snack Attack, <span>meriendas escolares</span> que sí se comen enteras</h2>
      <p class="lead">Nuestro primer producto <em>by Tu Merienda</em>: meriendas pensadas para el recreo, preparadas con ingredientes frescos y de calidad. Ricas, nutritivas y hechas con amor, todos los días de clases.</p>
      <div class="chip-row">
        <span class="chip">🥗 Ingredientes frescos</span>
        <span class="chip">💪 Nutritivas</span>
        <span class="chip">😋 Ricas de verdad</span>
        <span class="chip">❤️ Preparadas con amor</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- LONCHERA / MENU SEMANAL -->
<section class="lonchera-section" id="menu">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span> Así se ve tu semana</div>
      <h2>Abre la lonchera del día</h2>
      <p>Cada día de colegio trae una merienda distinta. Elige un día y descubre qué le espera a tu hijo o hija.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="menu-shot-wrap reveal">
      <div class="phone-frame">
        <img class="menu-shot" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Menú semanal Snack Attack en la app Tu Merienda">
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="note-love hand" style="text-align:center; margin-top:22px;">preparado con amor, como en casa ✏️</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PLANES -->
<section class="planes" id="planes">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span> Suscripción</div>
      <h2>Un plan para cada familia</h2>
      <p>Contamos con planes semanales y mensuales, pensados según el ritmo de cada familia. Estos son nuestros planes:</p>
    </div>
    <div class="plans-showcase reveal">
      <div class="plans-mascot">
        <img class="plans-mascot-img" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Mascota Snack Attack señalando los planes">
        <div class="mascot-bubble">¡Elige tu plan!</div>
      </div>
      <ul class="plan-pills">
        <li class="plan-pill">Beginner Plan</li>
        <li class="plan-pill">Plan Snack Start</li>
        <li class="plan-pill">Plan Power Snack</li>
        <li class="plan-pill">Plan Mega Snack</li>
        <li class="plan-pill">Plan Snack Legend</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p style="text-align:center; max-width:560px; margin:26px auto 0; color:#4b5180; font-size:.95rem;">Suscríbete para conocer el detalle y el precio de cada plan según las necesidades de tu familia.</p>
